Cathleen Cordell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cathleen_Cordell 0 Cathleen Cordell (May 21, 1915 – August 19, 1997) was an American film and television actress. She was described as "a lass born in Brooklyn with an Irish name and an English accent; educated in India and France."
